### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/

###

### Get student 1
GET http://localhost:3000/api/alunos/1

###

### Get student 1 agendamentos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/alunos/1/agendamentos

###

### Get all available slots
GET http://localhost:3000/api/slots

###

### Create a new agendamento
POST http://localhost:3000/api/agendamentos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alunoId": 3,
  "slotId": 3,
  "tipoAtendimento": "cronograma",
  "especificacao": "Noturno"
}

###

### Try to book the same slot again (should return 409)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/agendamentos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alunoId": 1,
  "slotId": 3,
  "tipoAtendimento": "simulado",
  "especificacao": "FUVEST"
}

### Cancel agendamento 1
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/agendamentos/1/cancelar

###

### Try to cancel it again (should return 409)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/agendamentos/1/cancelar

### Join waiting list
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lista-espera
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alunoId": 2,
  "turnoPreferencial": "Vespertino",
  "diasPreferencia": "Segunda ou Terca"
}

###

### Try to join again (should return 409)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lista-espera
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alunoId": 2,
  "turnoPreferencial": "Vespertino"
}

###

### Leave waiting list
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/lista-espera/1

### Join waiting list
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lista-espera
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alunoId": 2,
  "turnoPreferencial": "Vespertino",
  "diasPreferencia": "Segunda ou Terca"
}